title: 10 People Who Chose to Live in Some Unexpected Places

media:group.media:title: 10 People Who Chose to Live in Some Unexpected Places
media:group.media:description:
For most of us in the Western world, life follows a predictable path, at least in a very basic sense. You live with your family; you go to school; you get a job; you get your own home.

But some people just need to march to the beat of a different drum and that includes how they decide where they’re going to hang their hats at night. Let’s take a look at 10 of the most unexpected places people have chosen to live.
